query:
select count(*)
             from units u
             inner join collisions c on c.owner_id = u.fandom_id and u.language_id = c.collision_id
             where c.collision_type = $1 and u.status = $2 and
                   u.unit_type = $3 and c.value_1 = $4 and
                   u.date_create >= c.collision_date_create
